Sunshine State Games SATURDAY: Everyone got in and lapped a few @ 7:15 and then went to the big pool for figure warm ups. i was #40...next to Alyssa and Stefania.  Before duet warm ups michelle and i got into our suits and make up and then afterwards on the way to the bathrrom i ran into Alexa and her mommy then soon after Ryan saw me! The day ended with the beginning of my age group with the lightning...but I had my best figure meet ever this year!! 
SUNDAY: Lapped real quick around 6:50 then swam duet and got ready for team. Everyone said that we had a realy good team siwm through!

Today was okay. Had fun @ tennis but i got my period when I came home =\. Then my gram fixed my trio/duet suit for saturday...so thats good! Then @ practice I realized that the team I am swimming with now is all leaving next year.  This weekend is my last meet with them, i dunno its kinda depressing. That was mainly my day.  Not to mention the practice tonight really sucked! It rained so now i feel totaly unpreparred for this weeknd..::sigh:: we'll see what happens. 

~Martie~

I had a lot of fun today too! First I woke up and then came online and talk to matt for a while!!!! =) Then i ate breakfast and started to clean my room and all that stuff for the summer. Then I took a shower and got dressed cuz my gramsie took me and Adam to see "Mr. & Mrs. Smith"..I LOVED it!! After the movie we walked to Joanns to get some stuff for this board I'm gonna make! From the bar-mitzvah yesturday he was my last friend from hebrew school to have his bar-mitzvah so it was like my last time to see everyone because no one is comming back next year. Thinking about it really made me said and stuff so I asked matt this mornin if he thought we'd ever see eachother again if he didn't go to hebrew school next year and he said "I'll find a way don't worry" that made me feel really good like maybe its not the end but i hope he means it! xoxo
~Martie~

Oh my gosh Yesturday (Saturday) was awesome! First I went to practice and left eary @ 10:30. Then at 11:15 I went to Temple to see basically the most important part of Matt's Bar-Mitzvah service! He did good! Then after the brunch he had my gramps picked me up and on the way home we picked up Cristina so she could straighten my hair for the party! {it looked good until probably the very end of the party} At 5:00 I left with my gramsie to go to publix because I didn't have a card and I wanted to get a camera! By then it was 5:15 so we picked up Amy & Alyssa and went to the Mariott @ Heron Bay to get on the bus taking us to matt's Party! The party was aweseom, I had so much fun! I met like 3 new people but w/e it was all good! Then @ 12:30 am, Amy & Alyssa's dad picked us up to bring us back from the bus. Then I came home, watvhed TV and went to sleep!

LoL Today wasn't as bad as I thought it was going to be! At Tennis we only played and stuff in the morning and after lunch we went bowling! I came home basically did nothing and then after dinner I got ready for Temple....I went to Matt's friday night service!! Tomorow is gonna be aweseom!! xoxo

~Martie~

It wasn't too bad I guess- I woke up, watched tv, ate breakfast, waited for my grams to come home from her hair appointment so we could pack for camp.  When she did get home, we packed for like 4 hours because we had to get all of my clothes and than I either had to stamp of sew my name on every single peice of clothing! lol w/e hopefully it'll be worth it!? Then I walked around my house and finaly laid down and read my magazine. Now im here basically doin nuthin. tomore i have a busy day...I'll write bout it then! xoxo

~Martie~

I totally can't belive that this was the last day of school! Now I'm in 8th grade...woo hoo (sarcastic). I hope next year was like this year but maybe a lil better!?. Well after I ran around lunch gettin people to sign my shirt, we had a 7th grade food fight! LoL..I just hope we're not punished next year =\ we'll see. After school Jillian and I went over to Gaby's house to hang and stuff. I left around 3 cuz I was supposed to go to Ahsley's and lizzie's end of the year party but so far my grams is makin me go to practice when theres probably only gonna be a couple of people...w/e i'll deal.  Well I have absolutely nuthin to do cuz the part like just sarted, maybe we'll get to leave practice early.  I got a 94% on my math final, pretty happy bout that...not a bad year! xoxo

~Martie~

Today was so much better than yesturday!!! First in science we played jepordy to review for the final...lol bette study! then in math, the first part of the final was SO easy!! Lunch was good, tco day ain't too bad! In l.a it was alright, have to memorize stuff for the final on tuesday =\...oh well and in geo, movie on Antarctica...not too bad, lol Rachel i LUVED ur hair!! lol ! Now i just got home...i checked on pennacle 95 ON MY SPANISH FINAL!! lol stress is over, woot woot! lol well i g2g study n crap..kinda hopin practice will be canceled =|, lol if not oh well...much luv..xoxo
